{"id":173,"parent_id":158,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":173,"title":"Deuteronomy 15","subtitle":"","short_title":"Deut.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/15","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 15"],[".studySummary",["i","Every seven years, all debts are to be released—The people are admonished to care for the poor—Hebrew servants are to be released and given gifts during the seventh year—The firstling males of herds and flocks are the Lord’s."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/15.1","order":"02.06.015.15652"},["b","1"],"At the end of",["i","every"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"seven"],"years thou shalt make a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"release"],"."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/15.2","order":"02.06.015.15653"},["b","2"],"And this",["i","is"],"the manner of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"release"],": Every creditor that lendeth",["i","ought"],"unto his neighbour shall release",["i","it;"],"he shall not exact",["i","it"],"of his neighbour, or of his brother; because it is called the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"’s release."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/15.3","order":"02.06.015.15654"},["b","3"],"Of a foreigner thou mayest exact",["i","it again:"],"but",["i","that"],"which is thine with thy brother thine hand shall release;"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/15.4","order":"02.06.015.15655"},["b","4"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"Save"],"when there shall be no poor among you; for the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"shall greatly bless thee in the land which the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God giveth thee",["i","for"],"an inheritance to possess it:"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/15.5","order":"02.06.015.15656"},["b","5"],"Only if thou carefully hearken unto the voice of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God, to observe to do all these commandments which I command thee this day."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/15.6","order":"02.06.015.15657"},["b","6"],"For the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God blesseth thee, as he promised thee: and thou shalt lend unto many nations, but thou shalt not",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"borrow"],"; and thou shalt reign over many nations, but they shall not reign over thee."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/15.7","order":"02.06.015.15658"},["b","7"],"¶If there be among you a poor man of one of thy brethren within any of thy",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"gates"],"in thy land which the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God giveth thee, thou shalt not",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"harden"],"thine heart, nor shut thine hand from thy",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_7c"},"poor"],["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_7d"},"brother"],":"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/15.8","order":"02.06.015.15659"},["b","8"],"But thou shalt open thine",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"hand"],"wide unto him, and shalt surely lend him sufficient for his need,",["i","in that"],"which he",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"wanteth"],"."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/15.9","order":"02.06.015.15660"},["b","9"],"Beware that there be not a thought in thy wicked heart, saying, The seventh year, the year of release, is at hand; and thine",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"eye"],"be evil against thy poor brother, and thou givest him nought; and he",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"cry"],"unto the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"against thee, and it be sin unto thee."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/15.10","order":"02.06.015.15661"},["b","10"],"Thou shalt surely give him, and thine heart shall not be grieved when thou givest unto him: because that for this thing the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God shall bless thee in all thy works, and in all that thou puttest thine hand unto."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/15.11","order":"02.06.015.15662"},["b","11"],"For the poor shall never cease out of the land: therefore I command thee, saying, Thou shalt open thine",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"hand"],"wide unto thy brother, to thy poor, and to thy needy, in thy land."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/15.12","order":"02.06.015.15663"},["b","12"],"¶",["i","And"],"if thy brother, an Hebrew man, or an Hebrew woman, be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"sold"],"unto thee, and serve thee six years; then in the seventh year thou shalt let him go free from thee."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/15.13","order":"02.06.015.15664"},["b","13"],"And when thou sendest him out free from thee, thou shalt not let him go away empty:"],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/15.14","order":"02.06.015.15665"},["b","14"],"Thou shalt furnish him liberally out of thy flock, and out of thy",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"floor"],", and out of thy winepress:",["i","of that"],"wherewith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God hath blessed thee thou shalt give unto him."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/15.15","order":"02.06.015.15666"},["b","15"],"And thou shalt",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"remember"],"that thou wast a bondman in the land of Egypt, and the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God redeemed thee: therefore I command thee this thing to day."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/15.16","order":"02.06.015.15667"},["b","16"],"And it shall be, if he say unto thee, I will not go away from thee; because he loveth thee and thine house, because he is well with thee;"],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/15.17","order":"02.06.015.15668"},["b","17"],"Then thou shalt take an awl, and thrust",["i","it"],"through his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"ear"],"unto the door, and he shall be thy servant for ever. And also unto thy maidservant thou shalt do likewise."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/15.18","order":"02.06.015.15669"},["b","18"],"It shall not seem hard unto thee, when thou sendest him away free from thee; for he hath been",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"worth"],"a double hired servant",["i","to thee,"],"in serving thee six years: and the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God shall bless thee in all that thou doest."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/15.19","order":"02.06.015.15670"},["b","19"],"¶All the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"firstling"],"males that come of thy herd and of thy flock thou shalt",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_19b"},"sanctify"],"unto the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God: thou shalt do no work with the firstling of thy",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_19c"},"bullock"],", nor shear the firstling of thy sheep."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/15.20","order":"02.06.015.15671"},["b","20"],"Thou shalt eat",["i","it"],"before the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God year by year in the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"place"],"which the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"shall choose, thou and thy household."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/15.21","order":"02.06.015.15672"},["b","21"],"And if there be",["i","any"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"blemish"],"therein,",["i","as if it be"],"lame, or blind,",["i","or have"],"any",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_21b"},"ill"],"blemish, thou shalt not",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_21c"},"sacrifice"],"it unto the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/15.22","order":"02.06.015.15673"},["b","22"],"Thou shalt eat it within thy gates: the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"unclean"],"and the clean",["i","person shall eat it"],"alike, as the roebuck, and as the hart."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/15.23","order":"02.06.015.15674"},["b","23"],"Only thou shalt not eat the blood thereof; thou shalt pour it upon the ground as water."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/15.1a","order":"02.06.015.15675"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sabbatical-year"},"TG Sabbatical Year"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/15.1b","order":"02.06.015.15677"},["b","1b"],["span.small","IE"],"pardoning or cancellation of debts."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/15.2a","order":"02.06.015.15679"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/31.10"},"Deut. 31:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/15.4a","order":"02.06.015.15681"},["b","4a"],["span.small","HEB"],"To the end that there may be no needy."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/15.6a","order":"02.06.015.15683"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/borrow"},"TG Borrow"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/15.7a","order":"02.06.015.15685"},["b","7a"],["span.small","IE"],"cities, towns (also",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/15.22"},"v. 22"],")."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/15.7b","order":"02.06.015.15687"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/hardheartedness"},"TG Hardheartedness"],"."],["div",{"id":"7c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/15.7c","order":"02.06.015.15689"},["b","7c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/poor"},"TG Poor"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/welfare"},"Welfare"],"."],["div",{"id":"7d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/15.7d","order":"02.06.015.15691"},["b","7d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/brotherhood-and-sisterhood"},"TG Brotherhood and Sisterhood"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/15.8a","order":"02.06.015.15693"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/almsgiving"},"TG Almsgiving"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/15.8b","order":"02.06.015.15695"},["b","8b"],["span.small","HEB"],"needs."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/15.9a","order":"02.06.015.15697"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/88.67.67-68"},"D&C 88:67 (67–68)"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/15.9b","order":"02.06.015.15699"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/24.15"},"Deut. 24:15"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/15.11a","order":"02.06.015.15701"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/generosity"},"TG Generosity"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/15.12a","order":"02.06.015.15703"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/25.39.39-43"},"Lev. 25:39 (39–43)"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/15.14a","order":"02.06.015.15705"},["b","14a"],["span.small","OR"],"threshing floor."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/15.15a","order":"02.06.015.15707"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/7.12"},"Matt. 7:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/15.17a","order":"02.06.015.15709"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/21.6"},"Ex. 21:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/15.18a","order":"02.06.015.15711"},["b","18a"],["span.small","IE"],"at half the cost of a hired worker."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/15.19a","order":"02.06.015.15713"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/13.2"},"Ex. 13:2"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/2.3"},"Mosiah 2:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"19b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/15.19b","order":"02.06.015.15715"},["b","19b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/22.2"},"Lev. 22:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"19c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/15.19c","order":"02.06.015.15717"},["b","19c"],["span.small","HEB"],"cattle."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/15.20a","order":"02.06.015.15719"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/12.5.5-6"},"Deut. 12:5 (5–6)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/8.29.26-30"},"1 Kgs. 8:29 (26–30)"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/15.21a","order":"02.06.015.15721"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/22.20"},"Lev. 22:20"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/1.19.18-20"},"1 Pet. 1:19 (18–20)"],"."],["div",{"id":"21b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/15.21b","order":"02.06.015.15723"},["b","21b"],["span.small","OR"],"serious."],["div",{"id":"21c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/15.21c","order":"02.06.015.15725"},["b","21c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sacrifice"},"TG Sacrifice"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/15.22a","order":"02.06.015.15727"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/12.15"},"Deut. 12:15"],"."]]}
